            "message": "Dr Hector-Goma, congratulations on your 60th birthday. God bless your new age. As your days so shall your strength be. I want appreciate God\u2019s grace on your marriage. It\u2019s been 30 years of God\u2019s blessings and mercy. God is good and more grace to you and to our dear sister Dupe for the years ahead together. Happy anniversary. And we look forward to celebrating decades of God\u2019s favours with you in years and decades to come. \ud83d\ude4f\u2764\ufe0f",
            "name": "Pastor Bunmi and Jumoke Omodeinde",
            "relationship": ""
        },
        {
            "created_at": "2025-11-29 18:54:07",
            "id": 2,
            "message": "We have known Dr Ibiye Goma for almost 2 decades now. We strongly align with the kind words and testimony of everyone at 60-30 party on the 29th December,  2025. He is a wonderful gentleman with a big heart. Sis Dupe is a perfect fit for Dr Ibiye. Congratulations to both of you. We are blessed for knowing you. ",
            "name": "Tayo & Ronke",
            "relationship": "Friend "
        },
        {
