            "message": "Congratulations to your 60-30 celebration of life together. With love and affection we wish you and the family a day full of thanksgiving, laughter, health, and joy, celebrating the journey, wisdom and experiences that come with HBD age 60 yrs (Dr Abiye) and marriage 30 yrs with Modupe. The LORD continue to bless your union in Jesus name Amen. Amaopusenibo Prof Mike Sonny\u2764\ufe0f\ud83c\udf39\ud83c\udf7e\ud83c\udf81\ud83e\udd42\ud83d\ude4f",
            "name": "Amaopusenibo Prof MS & Mrs Ngozi Ijoma Sonny",
            "relationship": "Wakiriki Family community"
        },
