        {
            "created_at": "2025-11-28 13:45:37",
            "id": 7,
            "message": "Happy 30th Wedding Anniversary to you both, and a joyful 60th birthday celebration!\n \nToday marks not just a milestone of years but a beautiful testimony of love, partnership, strength, and unwavering commitment. Your journey together continues to inspire everyone privileged to know you.\n\nI want to take a moment to say something from the deepest part of my heart: thank you. Many years ago, your kindness changed the direction of my life in a moment when I felt I had run out of options. At a time when I was almost homeless with a newborn and a five-year-old, you stepped in with generosity, compassion, and love\u2014helping me secure a roof over our heads and giving us the safety and stability we desperately needed. I will never forget that. You didn\u2019t just offer help; you restored hope.\n\nAs you celebrate 30 years of marriage\u2014three decades of grace, love, and unity\u2014and as we rejoice with you on this special 60th birthday, I pray your home continues to overflow with peace, joy, health, laughter, and God\u2019s enduring blessings. May the years ahead be even more beautiful than all the years behind you.\n\nThank you for being a shining example of what true love, true friendship, true kindness and leadership look like.\nI celebrate you both today and always.\n\nWith gratitude,\nEsther",
            "name": "Esther Sample",
            "relationship": "Family Friend"
        },
        {
